Package: fiesta-can-bridge
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-paho-mqtt
Description: Ford Fiesta MK5 MS-CAN bridge — GVRET live decoder and MQTT publisher
 Connects to a GVRET-compatible CAN interface (e.g. WiCAN) over TCP,
 decodes MS-CAN frames from a Ford Fiesta MK5 (>2006), and publishes
 telemetry to an MQTT broker. Includes auto-discovery of the WiCAN
 device via dnsmasq DHCP lease file and a systemd service for
 unattended operation on a Raspberry Pi (carpi).
